                "invention-title": [
                    "Nuclear-based integrated energy system for high and cold remote areas and working method of nuclear-based integrated energy system",
                    "一种高寒边远地区核基综合能源系统及其工作方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a high and cold remote area nuclear-based comprehensive energy system and a working method thereof. The system comprises a high-temperature helium power generation subsystem, a medium-temperature steam power generation subsystem, a low-temperature waste heat power generation and heat supply subsystem, a high-temperature solid oxide water electrolysis hydrogen and oxygen preparation subsystem and a renewable energy power generation subsystem. One part of high-temperature and high-pressure helium exhausted from the gas cooled reactor enters the first steam generator to generate high-temperature steam for preparing hydrogen and oxygen, and the other part of the high-temperature and high-pressure helium enters the helium turbine for power generation; helium exhausted from the helium turbine enters the second steam generator to generate water vapor to drive the steam turbine to generate power; waste heat of working media from the steam turbine, the helium turbine and the electrolytic tank is collected, heat supply is conducted in the heating season, and power generation is conducted in the non-heating season. According to the invention, nuclear energy, solar energy and wind energy are combined to realize the zero-carbon target of energy supply, the influence of unstable wind energy and solar energy on energy supply is solved, and the requirements of high and cold remote areas on electricity, heat and oxygen are met."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开一种高寒边远地区核基综合能源系统及其工作方法，该系统包括高温氦气发电子系统、中温蒸汽发电子系统、低温余热发电和供热子系统、高温固体氧化物电解水制取氢气和氧气子系统和可再生能源发电子系统。从气冷堆排出的高温高压的氦气，一部分进入第一蒸汽发生器产生高温水蒸气用于制取氢气和氧气，另一部分进入氦气透平进行发电；从氦气透平排出的氦气进入第二蒸汽发生器，产生水蒸气驱动蒸汽轮机发电；收集来自汽轮机、氦气透平、电解池工质的余热，在供暖季进行供热，在非供暖季进行发电。本发明结合了核能、太阳能、风能实现了供能的“零碳”目标，并解决了风能和太阳能不稳定对供能的影响，并满足了高寒边远地区对电、热、氧的需求。"
                }
            ]
